
General
------------------------------------------

   #  Serialization Time,
      +  Can impact performance

   #  By default                 #156
      +  Spark uses 'Java Serialization' format
      
   #  Alternatively
      +  'Kryo' serializer can be used
      +  Provides 'fast' serialization over Java format
      +  Breadcrumb
         -  org.apache.spark.serializer.KryoSerializer
         -  Class Registration : spark.kryo.registrationRequired 


      